    question: '<h3>How much do you know about formatting text elements?</h3>\n<p>From the following code, match the proper HTML elements with the tags:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;p>\n  &#x3C;tag>\n   &#x3C;abbr title="Hypertext Markup Language">\n    HTML\n   &#x3C;/abbr>\n  &#x3C;/tag>\n  is the standard markup language\n  for creating web pages.\n&#x3C;/p>\n</code></pre>\n<p>tag: ???</p>\n',
